{"word":"G853 - ἀφανίζω - aphanízō - af-an-id'-zo - Corrupt","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀφανίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">aphanízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">af-an-id'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Corrupt</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வாடப்பண்ணு, கெடு, அழி, தோன்றாமற்போ"},{"paragraph":"to snatch out of sight, to put out of view, to make unseen"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G852 - ἀφανής - aphanḗs - af-an-ace'/852\">G852</a>; to <i>render unapparent</i>, that is, (actively) <i>consume</i> (<i>becloud</i>), or (passively) <i>disappear</i> (<i>be destroyed</i>): - corrupt, disfigure, perish, vanish away.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}